下食品公司專門販賣醃漬物，以新生薑系列產品受到許多日本人喜愛，社長岩下和了對於生薑有著異於常人的狂熱，在去年6月份還特別在栃木縣開設了「岩下新生薑博物館」，介紹公司的歷史與相關產品，其中最熱賣的紀念品「生薑手燈」，卻因為「騷擾女性」的理由宣布停產。<br />\n<br />\n根據日本《產經新聞》報導，岩下和了11日於推特表示，「生薑手燈」開賣之後，一直因為特殊的形狀，而被人質疑這是成人商品，日前有男性喝醉後使用來騷擾年輕女性，造成「淫穢和猥褻的嫌惡印象」，在煩惱後決定不再生產，感謝一直以來的支持。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n原文網址: 35公分「生薑手燈」大又粉嫩　形狀讓人想歪「GG」了 | ETtoday新奇 | ETtoday新聞雲 <a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20161016/794035.htm#ixzz54PRrfUiX\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20161016%2F794035.htm%23ixzz54PRrfUiX&d=oJc%2BoIJJC6h83Z5gWO3x3IzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=cdea8bea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20161016/794035.htm#ixzz54PRrfUiX</a> <br />\nFollow us: @ETtodaynet on Twitter | ETtoday on Facebook"},{"pid":"0315d48eefad51a9690b9cd36846ea41e8d74e4d","tid":530722,"uid":57844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fae773a95a3b8b33c4a4008d5209af219393693b","tid":530722,"uid":24576,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"041a398eff24918a82b39542ddb1b2240df702ea","tid":530722,"uid":71884,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T15:36:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/CGveghnUAAEdAZt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FCGveghnUAAEdAZt.jpg&h=cd7eba57&s={SIZE}\" />　生薑棒"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T03:29:14.000Z","msg":"即係咩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T03:36:53.000Z","msg":"螢光棒"},{"pid":"f26e72714b34dc8fc66210048daafd784c421c0b","tid":530722,"uid":147242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fae773a95a3b8b33c4a4008d5209af219393693b","tid":530722,"uid":24576,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"041a398eff24918a82b39542ddb1b2240df702ea","tid":530722,"uid":71884,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T15:36:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/CGveghnUAAEdAZt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%